| AI integration | Stable business API endpoint plus workflow adapter |
| Best for | More interactive list filtering |
| Main risk | More browser test surface |
| Demo cost | Medium |

## Option 3 - Persistence-First Admin

| Dimension | Decision |
|-----------|----------|
| Architecture | Flask + local JSON persistence + admin pages |
| AI integration | Workflow adapter writes normalized results back to storage |
| Best for | Repeatable records across restarts |
| Main risk | More state-reset work |
| Demo cost | Medium |

## Recommendation

- Recommended option: Option 1 - Fast Flask Admin
- Reason: enough for the primary loop and keeps dependency risk low
- Tradeoff accepted: repair records reset on restart

